The '''Dodge Attitude''' is a [[Rebadging|badge engineered]] [[subcompact car|subcompact]] [[sedan (car)|sedan]] sold by [[Dodge]] in Mexico over three generations since 2006. Dodge [[rebadging|rebadged]] the [[Hyundai Accent#MC|Hyundai Accent (MC)]] for the original version, updating the model line in 2011 with the [[Hyundai Accent#RB|RB series Accent]]. [[Mitsubishi Motors]] became the source of the Dodge Attitude from January 2015, using the [[Mitsubishi Mirage#Attrage|Mitsubishi Mirage sedan (Attrage)]] as the donor car.

